{"tid":860093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"各地破產嘅情況","createTime":"2018-10-13T05:33:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-14T04:01:50.000Z","uid":104109,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a3c15d82ce011c829144d6010709fa510f49ba1c","tid":860093,"uid":104109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:33:32.000Z","msg":"比定心理準備大家，睇下世界各地公營機構癱瘓/面臨破產嘅情況<br />\n<br />\n中國湖南耒陽：<br />\n<br />\nGDP曾穩居湖南省內五強的耒陽市，是湖南省城區面積最大、城市人口最多的縣級城市，是中國百強產煤市（縣）之一，可是，內地媒體報道地的年來財政收入持續惡化，同時反映地方債務的問題嚴重。<strong>耒陽市的公務員原訂上月15日發放的工資，至本月仍未發放</strong>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180615/58321709\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58321709&d=pEZI3lDOW5PHS5Aq%2FwRrlGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=83103d41\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180615%2F58321709&h=56099701\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/realtime/article/20180615/58321709</a><br />\n<br />\n江蘇鎮江﹕<br />\n<br />\n退休老兵冇退休金，重要比現役警察人打。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cA4umRa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcA4umRa.jpg&h=39bfe3db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180624/1378804/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180624%2F1378804%2F&d=pEZI3lDOW5PHS5Aq%2FwRrlGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=055c81ee\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fnew%2Frealtime%2F20180624%2F1378804%2F&h=1d68fcec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/new/realtime/20180624/1378804/</a><br />\n<br />\n希臘：<br />\n<br />\n推行左14輪緊縮措施，當中有 <br />\n1. 加稅，奢侈品稅加10%，進口車稅加10%，企業稅加3%，增加商品稅(包括食物，能源，藥物)<br />\n2. 調低稅階，由年收入&euro;12,000減至&euro;5,000都要交稅，高收入人士加稅<br />\n3. 延長退休年齡到67歲<br />\n4. 最低工資減22%<br />\n5. 公務員減30%人工，公營機構炒15萬人<br />\n6. 減教育開支，殺校，減醫療開支<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greek_austerity_packages\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fen.wikipedia.org%2Fwiki%2FGreek_austerity_packages&d=pEZI3lDOW5PHS5Aq%2FwRrlGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=ac875022\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Greek_austerity_packages</a> (詳細大家可以click入去慢慢欣賞)<br />\n<br />\n委內瑞拉<br />\n<br />\n政府冇錢就崩帶藥物手套都要自己買，個櫃咩都空嘅，冇藥冇抗生素，儀器壞左冇得用。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q11fivqZM1A\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3Dq11fivqZM1A&d=pEZI3lDOW5PHS5Aq%2FwRrlGi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=c54402a6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=q11fivqZM1A</a><br />\n<br />\n香港人做好準備面對上述嘅情況未? <br />\n<br />\n傳送門﹕香港破產嘅後果 <a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/857452/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/857452/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"e991cb058206c07f74e3372e119c74f2da019ded","tid":860093,"uid":163350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:34:26.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"056d36c0f03512114ed09aa5ac492ba2e8d8b260","tid":860093,"uid":19278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:37:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a82e1faee3c9a1732f3ca29a9cd3aff2ffae8e9","tid":860093,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T05:43:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92c9972f7bc3f7ed58ff2d42